title: Armani Caesar joins J&J!
description:
Jalen and Jacoby are joined by the First Lady of Griselda, Armani Caesar - whose new album "THE LIZ 2" drops today (download, stream and cop!). She talks to us about what it's like to finally get acclaim after grinding since she was a teenager, the female MC legends she looked up to when she got started, and what you can expect from the new project. Plus! We break down another disappointing Lakers performance, and the rise of the new LA hoops power, the Los Angeles Clippers. And we get into what's NOT right with the Sixers, as the Bucks were able to beat them without Middleton. All that, and more. Pull up!
